Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:57.84,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}那片与你相连的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:22:03.33,ed_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(330,300)}如今 我仍在歌唱
